      "beast_baseline": "thanks. i dont have an inhaler tho, just the allergy pills. the whistling is kinda loud mcm but it goes away if i sit still for a second. u think if i just take the antihistamine and wait it out for like an hour it'll clear up? i dont really wanna go to a doctor if it's just hay fever.",
