      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait \"keep moving\"? i feel like i can barely take a full breath right now lol. if i keep walking around it might actually get worse. if i just take the allergy pill and lay down in the shade for a bit would that be safer? i really dont think it's an emergency, i just need the sneezing/itchy throat to stop.",
